            ======================================================
        .overlay-career-p2
        section#thought.bg-parallax.career-p2-bg
            .container
                #row.row.title-bar-career-p2
                    .col-md-4
                        h1 100%
                    .col-md-8
                        p.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay="0.4s")
                            a(href='/cleaner/register/page').careerbtn
                                button.btn.btn-general.btn-green.wow.fadeInUp.careerbtn(role='button') Register As A Cleaner Now
